{# templates/home.html.twig #}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Zoo Arcadia - Accueil</title>
    <style>
        /* Styles pour la page d'accueil */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f8ff 40%, #d5f3e5);
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 700px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin: 0 20px;
            color: #34495e;
        }

        /* Palette de couleurs pour Zoo Arcadia */
        h1, p {
            color: #1d8348;
        }

        /* Style pour le bouton */
        .explore-button {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background-color: #1d8348;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .explore-button:hover {
            background-color: #145a32;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0px 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .explore-button img {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
        }

        /* Style pour le footer */
        footer {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #666;
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
        }

        footer a {
            color: #1d8348;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            color: #145a32;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Bienvenue sur Zoo Arcadia !</h1>
<p>Plongez au cœur de la biodiversité et explorez notre engagement pour la conservation de la nature et la protection des espèces rares. Profitez d'une visite inoubliable et éducative à travers nos habitats.</p>
<a href="{{ path('nelmio_api_doc_controller.swagger_ui') }}" class="explore-button">
    <img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/50/ffffff/document.png" alt="Documentation Icon">
    Explorez notre documentation API
</a>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Zoo Arcadia. Tous droits réservés. | <a href="https://127.0.0.1:8000/api/doc">Contactez-nous</a></p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
